{
  "stem": "23572.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And after awhile, I got to know the people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they used to-- many times, they used to ask, the Italian police, how come you speak so good Italian?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Yeah, I was dressed as an-- I was dressed as an American officer.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I had all the paraphernalia except the buttons where it says US, you know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So if American-- American military police would get me, they could not say that I was impersonating an American officer, because certain insignia, I didn't have.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had some fake decorations.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was very impressive to the Italians.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They didn't know one thing from the other.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But an American, I would say immediately, this is not an American uniform.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I used to tell them I was-- I come from-- my parents are Italian.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was born in Brooklyn, New York.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that's where I learned Italian.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "At home, we spoke Italian.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You know, so that's a-- I have a--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were very nice.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They really didn't care that much.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We said, these are not smugglers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We get them in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they said, bring them over.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And sometimes, I had some tough times.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Some of these-- some of these refugees, you know, they were fighting among themselves.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I said, shut, shut, quiet.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "This was 5 o'clock in the morning on a train.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Other people are going, and don't-- don't make too much noise.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I used to get them to Milan.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And in Milan, another group took over.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I usually had about 50.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's all I could take, 50.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, put them on the army trucks. 50 people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So this was my-- my job with the-- with the Bricha and Haganah.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this lasted until about 1946.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In 1946, I was [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
